                {
                    "title": "<span style=\"font-size:26px;\">&nbsp;</span>",
                    "content": "<div class=\"references\">\n<h1>Sources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://unstats.un.org/sdgs/indicators/database/\" target=\"_blank\">United Nations Department for Economic and Social Affairs (UNDESA), Statistics Division, Global SDG Indicators Database</a> (accessed July 2020).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://data.unicef.org/topic/child-protection/violence/\" target=\"_blank\">United Nations Children\u2019s Fund (UNICEF), latest data (2012 \u2013 2019)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.unicef.org/protection/files/Together_for_Girls_Sexual_Violence_Fact_Sheet_July_2012.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">UNICEF, Together for Girls: Sexual Violence Fact Sheet, July 2012</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n",
                    "contentActions": [],
